short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save and load drug lists from medicare.gov.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Script Keeper is a tool for saving and loading drug lists that are built using the medicare.gov site. Script Keeper aims to improve drug list building workflow by making it quick and easy to save anonymous drug list information
